{"tid":1695620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"One Piece 劇情 現實版 = 新疆集中營","createTime":"2019-11-05T17:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T12:57:30.000Z","uid":42246,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bff13f64cb15ef922333a00567aa3f6febf405fd","tid":1695620,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:37:45.000Z","msg":"op<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GdFUuR6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGdFUuR6.png&h=1bcc4f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DL2S0YN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDL2S0YN.png&h=c45a5a08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現實<br />\n<br />\n好撚恐怖 新疆集中營 女既被人輪姦 男既被生化實驗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670939</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#1<br />\n失望的熊貓<br />\n&bull; 10-23<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/china-xinjiang-uighur-muslim-detention-camps-xi-jinping-persecution-a9165896.html?utm_source=reddit.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fchina-xinjiang-uighur-muslim-detention-camps-xi-jinping-persecution-a9165896.html%3Futm_source%3Dreddit.com&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=a4ad1cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/china-xinjiang-uighur-muslim-detention-camps-xi-jinping-persecution-a9165896.html?utm_source=reddit.com</a><br />\n<br />\n之前都傳過 但係今次有逃亡人士出嚟指證<br />\n有女被人輪姦 所有人要睇住 合埋眼 表現嬲既話會被消失<br />\n所有靚女會被帶走 之後唔會再見返佢地<br />\n每日只有2分鐘去廁所 要被迫食藥打針<br />\n男既不舉 女既停經<br />\n記住內地官媒點樣描述香港示威<br />\n<br />\n恐怖主義既苗頭 港獨<br />\n<br />\n劇本已經寫好啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩者有咩分別？"},{"pid":